data.title: Netflix Titles
data.meta_description: netflix_titles (1) - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains a list of titles of movies and TV shows along with their durations in minutes. There are over 200 entries listing titles from Norm of the North: King Sized Adventure to Gol along with whether they are a movie or TV show and their duration in minutes. The durations range from 10 minutes to 182 minutes and include many movies and TV show titles across different genres.
